title: Julie Andrews, Randy Quaid, Zach Galifianakis: Oct. 1 celebrity birthdays
text:
By the Associated Press
Published: Oct. 1, 2015 Updated: 3:02 p.m. Is today your birthday? Here are a few celebrities you're celebrating with:
Actress-singer Julie Andrews is 80.
Actress Stella Stevens is 77.
Actor Stephen Collins ("7th Heaven") is 68.
Actor Randy Quaid is 65.
Singer Howard Hewett is 60.
Singer Youssou N’Dour is 56.
Actor Esai Morales ("NYPD Blue") is 53.
Actor Christopher Titus ("Titus") is 51.
Model-actress Cindy Margolis is 50.
Actor Zach Galifianakis ("The Hangover") is 46.
Actress Sarah Drew ("Grey’s Anatomy") is 35.
Actress Brie Larson ("United States of Tara") is 26.
Birthdays of the past:
1881 William Edward Boeing , Boeing Co. founder; died 1956.
1920 Walter Matthau , actor; died 2000.
